traits.description:
Final damage increased by **13%**.

When **3** volt weapons are equipped, get a **6%** volt damage increase.

Final damage increased by **18%**.

When **3** volt weapons are equipped, get a **6%** volt damage and crit rate increase.

The duration of the effect is increased by **25** seconds, triggering an explosion after the buff of the strike rate, you will get an additional **30** seconds of **18%** explosion damage bonus.
